description:
Jungle Killers!

According to law, you become a man when you're twenty one! But war has a habit of changing things! And sometimes you have to learn how to become a man in a hurry in the most dangerous classroom in the world -- patrolled by the most ruthless instructors of all times!

Operation Tall Tales

Aboard a C-54, a platoon of paratroopers wait expectantly for the order to jump! Their target -- a little town twenty miles south of Rome! They know that the country in which they are going to make their landing is alive with crack German troops -- the elite divisions of Nazi Field Marshal Albert Kesselring! But they don't know what lies ahead of them in... Operation Tall Tales

Devil Dogs of Chateau Thierry!

It is a hot sunny afternoon in May, the 30th to be exact, the year is 1918, you are a Sgt. in the 4th Marine Brigade of the American Second Division, you are riding in a truck toward a little French town on the river Marne. You don't know it yet -- but you're going to make history...

Three For Danger! (Text only story)

Ghost Squadron

This is an airfield in France... on the outskirts of a small village called Vaux Sur Somme! Its empty hangers... the weeds on its runway... show it to be abandoned... and long out of use! Yet... a man walks here -- unable to drive a nightmare out of his mind-- remembering a... Ghost Squadron
name: Jungle Killers!; Operation Tall Tales; Devil Dogs of Chateau Thierry!; Three For Danger!; Ghost Squadron
